{"tid":809151,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"ESPN消息　高普 已與 拉比奧特母親 展開聯繫　明年或免費簽到利物浦","createTime":"2018-09-07T02:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T07:42:49.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3852e3450eea1dbaa6e3c0f3f6311ff0c3faffeb","tid":809151,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T02:42:48.000Z","msg":"香港時間9月5日，據ESPN消息，高普已經與拉比奧特的母親和經理人展開聯繫，尋求在明年夏天以免簽的方式將他帶到英超。<br />\n<br />\n　　更有消息人士告知ESPN，高普已經與拉比奧特通過電話，談論轉會事宜。<br />\n<br />\n　　報導稱，高普在多蒙特時期就有意拉比奧特，而拉比奧特在去年10月份的採訪中表示，從小就非常喜歡利物浦，很樂意加盟英超。<br />\n<br />\n　　拉比奧特現年23歲，他與大巴黎的合同僅剩最後一年。此前他曾拒絕與巴黎續約，但巴黎方面還在一直尋求續約。巴塞、曼城等球會也有意引進拉比奧特。"},{"pid":"ea15b9ab288075df6fcf221c11f4714c24695ec3","tid":809151,"uid":28770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T02:43:45.000Z","msg":"地方的媽媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79f744c81802b274ef1b4acc25ecdc34cf7214fe","tid":809151,"uid":128568,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T02:49:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/s--aRbtJ6hK--/c_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,q_80,w_800/fihub8xetuvtsqzavkq2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kinja-img.com%2Fgawker-media%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fs--aRbtJ6hK--%2Fc_scale%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_80%2Cw_800%2Ffihub8xetuvtsqzavkq2.jpg&h=76182288&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06ca109eb5eb950cf0d0beaae7f13b73c886351b","tid":809151,"uid":96941,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T02:51:19.000Z","msg":"出年成隊利身浦應該比人買走埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"529868479946e23967e0b2c12be9bf0186e1f945","tid":809151,"uid":124667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06ca109eb5eb950cf0d0beaae7f13b73c886351b","tid":809151,"uid":96941,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T02:51